ast.source:
OTel tracing mode is active (via LANGSMITH_TRACING_MODE, OTEL_ENABLED, or LANGSMITH_OTEL_ENABLED), but the required OTEL instances have not been initialized. Please add:
```
import { initializeOTEL } from "langsmith/experimental/otel/setup";
initializeOTEL();
```
at the beginning of your code.

ast.target:
OTel 追踪模式已激活（通过 LANGSMITH_TRACING_MODE、OTEL_ENABLED 或 LANGSMITH_OTEL_ENABLED），但所需的 OTEL 实例尚未初始化。请在代码开头添加：
```
import { initializeOTEL } from "langsmith/experimental/otel/setup";
initializeOTEL();
```
